						               													<description>Are you a geek? Maybe even a little nerd? You love pixel art and fantasy but are too lazy to learn complex rules?  Then GRABLIN is for you!!! A fun dice game based on simple rules, to play with your friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Throw your dice! &amp;quot;Grab&amp;quot; the treasure and start running! GRABLIN is the dice game that mixes luck, greed, and cunning. Choose whether to risk it and grab more treasures, or to play it safe. Steal your adversaries treasures, but pay attention! Behind every corner there's always the risk of a red skull, ready to bust you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Rules:&amp;#10;A) Choose 3 DICE from the dice box, ROLL THEM, and add them to any other dice you've rolled so far this turn.&amp;#10;B) If you have 3 SKULLS showing, your turn ends; return all dice you've rolled this turn to the dice box.&amp;#10;C) If you have 3 FISTS showing, return them to the dice box in order to steal a TREASURE from another player, then go to STEP(D).&amp;#10;D) Otherwise, you may choose to go back to STEP(A) to continue rolling, or you may end your turn: for each group of 3 TREASURES showing on your dice, keep 1 TREASURE; return the other TREASURES and all FISTS and SKULLS to the dice box.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who gets 5 TREASURES first is the WINNER&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
